etat kriyākalāpaprasūtasya puṇyasya sarvasattvānāṃ buddhatvāya niryātanam ||

<commentary>praṇidhānaṃ saṃsārikasukhasaṃgam | bodhicittaṃ pāralaukikasukhāya cittaniyojanam | buddho bhaveyaṃ jagato hitāyeti kṛtvā namaskāram iti trividhaṃ kāyikaṃ vācanikaṃ mānasikaṃ ceti | tadraśmibhir iti svahṛdayasthitahūṃkāradīptibhiḥ ||</commentary>
